pkgmetadata.longdescription: Fixed Effects Logistic Model with High-Dimensional Parameters // A structured profile likelihood algorithm for the logistic fixed effects model and an approximate expectation maximization (EM) algorithm for the logistic mixed effects model. Based on He, K., Kalbfleisch, J.D., Li, Y. and Li, Y. (2013) doi:10.1007/s10985-013-9264-6.
